{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idaacdcafe-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6333"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6333"},"text":"§ 6333.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Funding for laboratory directed research and development","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding section 307 of the Energy and Water Development and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 2010 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/85"},"text":"Public Law 111–85","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/123/2845"},"text":"123 Stat. 2845","children":[],"tail":"), of the funds made available by the Department of Energy for activities at Government-owned, contractor-operated laboratories funded in the Energy and Water Development and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 2014 (div. D of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/76"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–76","children":[],"tail":") or any subsequent Energy and Water Development Appropriations Act for any fiscal year, the Secretary may authorize a specific amount, not to exceed 6 percent of such funds, to be used by such laboratories for laboratory directed research and development."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idaacdcaff-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/119/60/dC/tXXXI/s3111/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 119–60, div. C, title XXXI, § 3111(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2025-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 2025","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/139/1449"},"text":"139 Stat. 1449","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idaacdcb00-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idaacdcb01-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idaacdcb02-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 307 of the Energy and Water Development and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 2010, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/85/s307"},"text":"section 307 of Pub. L. 111–85","children":[],"tail":", title III, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2009-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 2009","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/123/2872"},"text":"123 Stat. 2872","children":[],"tail":", which is listed in a table of similar provisions under former "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s2791a"},"text":"section 2791a of Title 50","children":[],"tail":", War and National Defense."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Energy and Water Development and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 2014, referred to in text, is div. D of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/76"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–76","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2024-01-17"},"text":"Jan. 17, 2024","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/152"},"text":"128 Stat. 152","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"idaacdcb03-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 6333 was renumbered ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":